{"id":"812201684547878912","type":"text","timestamp":1774575886,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/812201684547878912","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/mysticsapphickitten/810693393188618240\">mysticsapphickitten</a>:</p><blockquote><p>I need someone to climb into my bed and hold me close to them. Let me bury my head into your chest whilst you caress my skin and whisper to me that everything’s going to be okay. </p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"mysticsapphickitten"},"post":{"id":"810693393188618240"}}],"baseline_notes":23,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}